You'll notice I've tended to say "can be Beta" in some of the above.  This is because it really does depend on the sequence.

Generally speaking, an Opener who has already LIMITED their hand by making an intermediate Opening will not normally have Beta available.  eg: 

^c 1H - 2@C - 3@D(Upper Range, 5 - 5+) - 3@H - ??? 

